{"tid":2477803,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人玩玩下MHR想返去玩MHW?","createTime":"2021-04-06T14:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T19:28:45.000Z","uid":14503,"like":40,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"3e352ae840db4caacc82a045d1db1aeffaea56b0","tid":2477803,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"認真討論講下感受非引戰。。。<br />\n話說最後聽巴打講話好玩就得，最後都係買左MHR都遇左畫面唔會好<br />\n咁一開始玩係駁電視用pro掣玩，玩曬d rank 1任就頂唔順<br />\n畫而唔係差而係好撚差，本身話佢得PS3畫面質素諗住係誇張啲講點知原來真係得PS3質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁佢個地圖係學mhw咁玩無縫但真係做得好差，一來個地圖好細冇乜高低位立體感一開波上狗向前推9直跑一陣就見到隻野，之後就開波打完全冇環境同氣氛。。。 有時隻野喺山上面你又要走到老連咁遠去搵條藤爬上去成日都冇位比你爬，mhw唔會做到咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個d 環境生物同埋植物出現嘅位置又奇奇怪怪好似格眼擺喺中間叫你過嚟拎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻怪個幾個定點走黎去雖然mhw都係咁但硬係覺得mhr悶好多好機械化相比mhw生動好多。仲有想講佢多左個d跳蟲動作多左野比你你操作但本身switch fps真係好低搞到d動作質下質下咁好唔流暢月 搞到唔想用呢啲花巧嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩左陣就覺得不如返去玩mhw好過，mhr真係比唔到更好既遊戲體驗， 有冇人玩咗一陣諗住不如返去玩mhw算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a782af8aa6537774151081ecbe37408859ed030a","tid":2477803,"uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"不如大家講下mhr好玩係邊？"},{"pid":"eb5afb4dcd71c637e3d35385f46